gomodel:SYNGO_260  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: >10fold-enriched in docked SV fraction (fig. 5)\n\n20/3/2017 Pim\n- Because enriched in AZ and not in free SV protein is presumably localized to the AZ, and not in co-purifying SVs.. Experimental description: Results: \"To isolate docking complexes from **rat brain**, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A).\"" ;
